librec-auto documentation¶

Quickstart guide¶

pip install librec-auto

The Code¶

class librec_auto.ConfigCmd(config_file, target)¶

Loads the configuration file using the element rules. Elements labels as “unparsed” in the rules are added to the _unparsed collection later processing.
